729444f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Treadwell Avenue
729444f-a.text:
Richmond Terrace, adjoining the S.E. corner
of Treadwell Avenue, showing St. Mary's Roman Catholic
Church. The house on the left, is the parish house.
May 22, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
Anether view of the church, and the neighboring
houses, as seen from the shore of the Kill Van Kull.
May 22, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(3)
An additional view, at a later date.
June 1, 1935
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
